<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师父和师弟们开始脸色发青，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>左右摇摆，悟空吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的头前后摇晃,</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>茶杯从手里掉了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，砰！唐僧摔倒在地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，悟净和八戒也昏了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个可恶的妖怪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空猛地站起来拿出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士向后退了一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，门开了。三个女人跑了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又是你们几个？”悟空大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人们朝悟空射蜘蛛丝，他一跳避开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到空中，翻了个跟头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>落在了三个女人后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿金箍棒猛打。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！一股烟出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>烟退去后，在一个女人的位置上躺着一只死蜘蛛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外两个女人吓得目瞪口呆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他打死了我们的姐妹！”一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是个怪物！”另一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空朝她们冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打掉了飞来的蜘蛛丝。嘣！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个女人都消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们那里躺着两只死蜘蛛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那几个蜘蛛精是我的好朋友！”道士喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛充满了愤怒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会后悔杀死她们的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士打开衣服，露出了身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那身体上有无数只眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那些眼睛放出金光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！金光太亮了！”悟空大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捂住自己的眼睛，在房间里到处跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，无法摆脱那刺眼的金光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他用金箍棒砸了道观的石地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上出现一个巨大的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到里面变成了鼹鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用爪子挖洞，一直挖，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>直到确定自己已经离道观很远。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空从地里蹦出来，变回了原样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金光从道观射来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然光离得很远，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但也让悟空的眼睛很痛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转过身去。“怎么办呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我没办法救师父和师弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那道士的金光太厉害了。”他开始哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199073</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，有个声音传来：“别哭，悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199074</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抬头看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一个高大的女人站在上方，低头看他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是毗蓝婆菩萨。”那女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个道士是蜈蚣精，叫做百眼魔君。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有我能打败他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毗蓝婆菩萨从袖子里拿出一个绣花针，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>转身把那个针扔向金光。轰隆！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那声音像天上打雷一样，金光消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和毗蓝婆菩萨一起来到道观。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士躺在地上，浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他所有的眼睛都紧紧地闭着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毗蓝婆菩萨用手指了一下道士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>道士变成了一条大蜈蚣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毗蓝婆菩萨从袖子里拿出一个瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你，悟空。”毗蓝婆菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些药丸能救你师父和师弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要带走蜈蚣，让他受罚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空行礼。“谢谢您，毗蓝婆菩萨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人继续西行。又过了几周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最近一路很顺利。”有一天，唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼笑了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“确实是。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妖怪们想吃师父的事情过去几周了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“西天还很远呢。”悟空提醒大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在到达那里之前，我们会遇到更多的危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧笑了。“别紧张，悟空，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>享受这美好的日子吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里没有危险。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一个男人出现在前方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拼命地挥动着胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别过来！”那男人大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那前面有危险！非常危险！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>